    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>创建ID 131虚拟机</p><pre class="line-numbers language-javascript" data-language="javascript"><code class="language-javascript">qm create <span class="token number">131</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p>把yj-131.qcow2 的镜像导入到local-lvm的lvm块上。 </p><pre class="line-numbers language-javascript" data-language="javascript"><code class="language-javascript">qm importdisk <span class="token number">131</span> yj<span class="token operator">-</span><span class="token number">131.</span>qcow2 local<span class="token operator">-</span>lvm<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p>解锁131 </p><pre class="line-numbers language-javascript" data-language="javascript"><code class="language-javascript">qm unlock <span class="token number">131</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p>把存储池local-lvm,lvm 块vm-131-disk-0分配给131的virtio0 磁盘，做系统盘。 </p><pre class="line-numbers language-javascript" data-language="javascript"><code class="language-javascript">qm <span class="token keyword">set</span> <span class="token number">131</span> <span class="token operator">--</span>virtio0 local<span class="token operator">-</span>lvm<span class="token operator">:</span>vm<span class="token operator">-</span><span class="token number">131</span><span class="token operator">-</span>disk<span class="token operator">-</span><span class="token number">0</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p>给wangguan组添加PVEAuditor（资源均可见只读）的权限。 </p><pre class="line-numbers language-javascript" data-language="javascript"><code class="language-javascript">pveum aclmod <span class="token operator">/</span> <span class="token operator">-</span>group wangguan <span class="token operator">-</span>role PVEAuditor<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><pre